**Purpose Statement**:
The UX Strategist transforms product specifications into user-centered design artifacts, including React/Tailwind prototypes, information architecture maps, accessibility-compliant interfaces, and validated user flows that ensure features are intuitive, inclusive, and aligned with product strategy.

